<h2>
<a id="user-content-gzip-size" class="anchor" href="#gzip-size" aria-hidden="true"><span aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link"></span></a>gzip-size</h2>
<p>The GZIP algorithm is available in different flavours and with different
possible compression settings. The sizes quoted in this README have been
